All Implemented Interfaces:
org.hamcrest.Matcher<Header>, org.hamcrest.SelfDescribing
public final class Rfc1123DateMatcher
extends org.hamcrest.TypeSafeMatcher<Header>

Matcher to check that headers contain dates which are spec-valid. All dates in HTTP headers (Date-header, caching, etc) should pass this matcher.
